                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/z1984s/">十三_接地气</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2010-03-15</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">好。</p>
